      # DYNASTY OWNER FAQS


      ##Can I have multiple dynasty owner teams?
      Just like in the NFL, owners can’t own multiple teams for a variety of reasons.
      We limit each person/account to one dynasty owner franchise because Dynasty Owner is a year round in- depth ownership experience that requires a lot more attention than managing a traditional fantasy football team.  We also want to ensure that nobody is managing multiple teams for the sake of just optimizing one.  Like it!

      ##How many teams are allowed per league?  What if we our league wants 10 teams or 14 teams?
      This year (2012-2013 season) we are restricting leagues to 12 teams per league.  This allows us to be fair in the efficiency payout grand prizes for both tiers.   If leagues had different numbers of teams, efficiency wouldn’t be an apples to apples comparison across entire tiers.  Like it!

      ##Why can’t I see weekly updates of efficiency leaders?
      We don’t want to encourage any collusion and above all want owners to run their teams individually and with competitive integrity.  The grand prize is large enough to where if one league saw that one of the teams was in contention for the grand efficiency prize, they might all agree to help that team maximize efficiency and split the grand prize.

      Along those lines, winners of the efficiency grand prize will be thoroughly reviewed to ensure that no collusion was suspected or evident.  I don’t mind mentioning this, but I don’t want to dare people to collude. We mention it already before. Maybe we should just the first part but not the second.

      ##When can I expect to be paid my weekly winnings?
      Weekly winnings will be paid out on Tuesday morning at 6 AM, after all games have been played for the previous week.

      ##When can I expect to be paid my end of season winnings?
      For those playing in the Championship game, you can expect your winning check within 4 weeks of the Championship game.  If you win the GRAND PRIZE, you can expect that within 8 weeks of the Championship game. As you can imagine, with such a large prize, we have to be thorough and make sure we are able to determine the winner.

